[
    {
        "text": "Before cleaning your mousepad,",
        "start": 0.833,
        "duration": 1.447
    },
    {
        "text": "your first step should be\nlooking up the manufacturer",
        "start": 2.28,
        "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
        "text": "and finding out what they\nrecommend as a cleaning method.",
        "start": 4.78,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "While mousepads made of a harder material,",
        "start": 8.06,
        "duration": 2.59
    },
    {
        "text": "like plastic or rubber,",
        "start": 10.65,
        "duration": 1.37
    },
    {
        "text": "can typically be washed\nusing a damp cloth,",
        "start": 12.02,
        "duration": 2.75
    },
    {
        "text": "mousepads made of cloth",
        "start": 14.77,
        "duration": 1.55
    },
    {
        "text": "may take some additional\nsteps to get clean.",
        "start": 16.32,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "Here is a method that could\nwork well with your mousepad.",
        "start": 18.64,
        "duration": 2.54
    },
    {
        "text": "Fill your sink with warm water",
        "start": 21.18,
        "duration": 1.825
    },
    {
        "text": "and submerge your mousepad.",
        "start": 25.58,
        "duration": 1.653
    },
    {
        "text": "Using a soft brush or sponge,",
        "start": 28.35,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "apply a small dab of mild dish soap",
        "start": 30.72,
        "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
        "text": "and then gently scrub the pad.",
        "start": 33.19,
        "duration": 1.793
    },
    {
        "text": "Then, rinse thoroughly.",
        "start": 36.16,
        "duration": 1.803
    },
    {
        "text": "Use a clean towel to help dry the pad,",
        "start": 40.34,
        "duration": 2.323
    },
    {
        "text": "then leave it out to\ndry for several hours.",
        "start": 44.82,
        "duration": 2.683
    },
    {
        "text": "Once it's completely dry,",
        "start": 48.55,
        "duration": 1.583
    },
    {
        "text": "enjoy your new, clean mousepad.",
        "start": 50.133,
        "duration": 3.2
    }
]